title: Rent controlled apt / 1 block from alamo sq park
posting_body: ['Rent controlled apartment!', 'Looking for min 6 months period ( Sept 1, 2022- End of Feb 2023).', ' Could be longer if we can cohabitate peacefully.', 'Large room with walk-in closet in a beautiful rent-controlled 2BR classic San Francisco apartment decorated with love.', 'The location gives you walking access to the best cafes and music venues, restaurants, workout places and more in the city like The Mill, The Independent, NOPA, Souvla, Corepower Yoga, and more, all within 2 blocks of the apartment.', 'Really convenient public transport access - 24 is 1 block, 5 is 2 blocks, and 7 is 4 small blocks away.', '420 friendly', 'Bonus: Great collection of books.', 'And the best movie recommendations.', '—-', 'The room is available starting Sept 1, 2022.', 'Single Bedroom 1 person ( no sharing)', '$1600Monthly Rent', 'Shared kitchen ( fully stocked)', 'Shared bathroom w/ the ( master tenant)', 'Washer & Dryer in building with convenient access', 'We will split utilities & internet access', 'Looking for clean quiet tenant', 'Must adhere to cleaning guidelines', 'The building has a no pet policy', 'To move in, need-', "deposit of one month's rent", 'Proof of income & ID', 'Will be doing a showing upon request.', 'Features:', '*Foyer', '*Large living room', '*Large bedroom', '*Mid-sized bathroom', '*Mid-sized kitchen', '*Additional storage space for luggage', '*Fully stocked kitchen', '*semi furnished']
